snippet.title: The Wild Eight - Version 1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
HypeTrain Digital's top selling survival action-adventure, The Wild Eight, is coming out or Early Access on October 3rd!

The Wild Eight is an intense survival action-adventure set in frozen wilderness of Alaska. Team up with friends in online co-op or go solo, explore the mysterious land, craft weapons and fight to live another day.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/526160/The_Wild_Eight/

Follow HypeTrain on social media:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/hypetraindigital/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/HypeTrainDgt
